data.description: Charming townhouse with 3 bedrooms & 2.5 bathrooms located in highly sought after gated community. Kitchen features quartz countertops with stainless steel appliances. Spacious living area with laminate stairs and hallway. One car garage with driveway for additional car parkings. Custom panel storm shutters. Walk in closet and dual sinks in master bedroom and bathroom.  Beautiful secure fenced in backyard, great for entertaining. 24 hour notice preferred for showings. Two HOAs yet affordable. ***BEING SOLD AS-IS***
